            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Depossio <note>sic</note> Vitalioni <note>sic</note> <lb n="2"/>innocentis qui vi<lb break="no" n="3"/>xit anno uno et men<lb break="no" n="4"/>sis <note>sic</note> quattuor et dies <expan><abbr>V</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan><supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied> <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>2 aneinanderpassende Fragmente erhalten. Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. Buchstabe A mit spitz nach unten zeigender Querhaste. Z. 4 (Ende): statt V auch X möglich. (B): Egger: Z. 4: DIES QV.</p>
            </div>
